## Tier 3 — Conventional (Game-Specific Compound Expressions)

These are valid UL constructions but are T3 design choices — compound expressions, not geometric necessities.

```yaml
tier_3_symbols:
  - ul_symbol: zigzag
    ul_primitive: [Line, Angle]
    ul_tier: T3
    ul_level: 3  # Two-primitive combination
    geometric_description: >
      A compound of Lines composed with alternating Angles.
      Piecewise linear with periodic angle inversions.
      Conventionally associated with agility and disruption.
    sigma_ul_expression: "compose(r1, invert(r1), compose(r2, invert(r2), ...))"
    movement_primitive: zigzag_dash
    animation_ref: zigzag_dash_anim
    glyph: "〽"
    phonetic: zɪɡzæɡ
    element: Air
    modality: Mutable
    cosmic_force: Flux

  - ul_symbol: leap
    ul_primitive: [Curve, Angle]
    ul_tier: T3
    ul_level: 3  # Two-primitive combination
    geometric_description: >
      A Curve (parabolic arc) with an Angle trajectory — directed aspiration
      reaching a peak and descending. Process with a distinguished angular character.
      Conventionally associated with breakthrough and courage.
    sigma_ul_expression: "modify_relation(m_aspiration, curve_parabolic)"
    movement_primitive: high_leap
    animation_ref: high_leap_anim
    glyph: "⤴"
    phonetic: liːp
    element: Fire
    modality: Cardinal
    cosmic_force: Power
```

---

## T3 Conventional: Element / Modality / Cosmic Force Mappings

The element, modality, and cosmic force fields are T3 — conventional game-layer semantic coordinates.
They are not wrong; they are useful design choices for organizing game logic.
Their real UL interpretation:

```yaml
t3_semantic_coordinates:
  elements:
    Fire: "Dominant quality: directed/transformative (Angle-dominant expressions)"
    Earth: "Dominant quality: structured/stable (Enclosure-dominant, D4 symmetry)"
    Water: "Dominant quality: continuous/process (Curve and Enclosure/circle dominant)"
    Air: "Dominant quality: relational/mobile (Line-dominant and compound expressions)"

  modalities:
    Cardinal: "Assertion dynamics: declarative — makes a definitive claim"
    Fixed: "Assertion dynamics: persistent — asserts a stable state"
    Mutable: "Assertion dynamics: processual — asserts ongoing change"

  cosmic_forces:
    Core: "Extremal angle: identity (theta=0 degrees, coincidence, agreement)"
    Order: "Extremal angle: independence (theta=90 degrees, orthogonality)"
    Chaos: "Extremal angle: opposition via oscillation (periodic inversion)"
    Void: "Maximum-symmetry empty enclosure (circle enclosing nothing)"
    Alpha: "Minimum-complexity enclosure (triangle = fundamental/irreducible)"
    Power: "Directed aspiration angle (non-perpendicular focused angle)"
    Flux: "Process with change: curve and spiral expressions"
    Omega: "Completion: theta=360 degrees, full cycle returning to start"
    Omni: "All-inclusive quantification (universal quantifier)"
```

